  "cover": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p0.jpg",
  "audio": null,
  "pages": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p1.jpg",
      "text": "Bibin se yon ti fi ki ap viv ak manman li Monik.\nTout moun renmen li paske li entelijant, saj, epi li bèl anpil."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p2.jpg",
      "text": "Yon jou Bibin ap sot lekòl, epi li wè yon ti chen.\nLi karese li, ti chen an tonbe souke ke li."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p3.jpg",
      "text": "Bibin leve pou li ale, men ti chen an tonbe swiv li.\nLè li rive lakay li, ti chen an te dèyè li."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p4.jpg",
      "text": "Manman li di: kote ou pran ti chen sa a?\nBibin di: nan wout la manman, li swiv mwen depi lekòl la."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p5.jpg",
      "text": "Bibin mande manman li si li ka pran chen an.\nManman li di: si li san mèt, ou ka pran li."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p6.jpg",
      "text": "Ti chen an dou, Monik tonbe karese li.\nMonik ak Bibin renmen lè li ap souke ke li."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p7.jpg",
      "text": "Ti chen an pran swiv manman Bibin.\nMonik ak Bibin renmen ti chen an."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/kendrajoseph1997%40gmail.com%2f5d5ec6d5-712c-416f-b569-2cd593ea44c4%2flittle+sally%2f4l1-p8.jpg",
      "text": "Bibin rele ti chen an \"Souke\"."
    }
  ],
